irectEnd</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/PerformanceTiming/redirectStart\"><code>redirectStart</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/PerformanceTiming/requestStart\"><code>requestStart</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/PerformanceTiming/responseEnd\"><code>responseEnd</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/PerformanceTiming/responseStart\"><code>responseStart</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/PerformanceTiming/secureConnectionStart\"><code>secureConnectionStart</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/PerformanceTiming/unloadEventEnd\"><code>unloadEventEnd</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/PerformanceTiming/unloadEventStart\"><code>unloadEventStart</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for Navigation Timing</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Performance\"><code>Performance</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/PerformanceNavigation\"><code>PerformanceNavigation</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/PerformanceNavigationTiming\"><code>PerformanceNavigationTiming</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/performance_property\"><code>performance_property</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"summary","title":"Summary","isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong><code>PerformanceTiming.connectEnd</code></strong> 这个只读属性返回一个无符号长整型，它以毫秒为单位，代表了网络链接建立的时间节点。如果传输层报告了错误或者链接又被重新建立，则采用最后一次链接建立的时间。如果链接是长久的，那么这个值等同于<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/PerformanceTiming/fetchStart\"><code>PerformanceTiming.fetchStart</code></a>。链接被认为打开以所有的链接握手，SOCKS 认证结束为标志。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>time</em> = <em>performanceTiming</em>.connectEnd;</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"Specifications","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/navigation-timing/#dom-performancetiming-connectend\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Navigation Timing<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">PerformanceTiming.connectEnd</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.PerformanceTiming.connectEnd","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/PerformanceTiming/connectEnd/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\">\n<div id=\"sect2\">\n<div id=\"sect3\">\n\n\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>参见 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/PerformanceTiming\"><code>PerformanceTiming</code></a> 接口。</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Summary","id":"summary"},{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"PerformanceTiming.connectEnd 这个只读属性返回一个无符号长整型，它以毫秒为单位，代表了网络链接建立的时间节点。如果传输层报告了错误或者链接又被重新建立，则采用最后一次链接建立的时间。如果链接是长久的，那么这个值等同于PerformanceTiming.fetchStart。链接被认为打开以所有的链接握手，SOCKS 认证结束为标志。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"PerformanceTiming.connectEnd","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"PerformanceTiming.connectEnd","locale":"fr","native":"Français"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/performancetiming/connectend","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/performancetiming/connectend/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/PerformanceTiming","title":"PerformanceTiming"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/PerformanceTiming/connectEnd","title":"PerformanceTiming.connectEnd"}],"pageTitle":"PerformanceTiming.connectEnd - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}